one of the worst videos iv seen 90% is just walking thru the pits talking to drivers that are doing useless crap. wish i could get my money back for this.

Thought this was gonna be like a 1320 video where it shows full races with info on the cars and owners not an hour long "trailer" of drag week with short clips of drag races and a handful of people talking about how much they love racing  very disappointed I wasted my money
someone got this for my 6 year old son, we both keep watching it over and over. we both love the soundtrac and the drag racing is awesome.
